.*       THE MACRO PROTOTYPE IS ABOVE                                 * 34000020
.*                                                                    * 36000020
.*                                                                    * 38000020
.*       THE STANDARD FORM OF THE EXPANSION IS BELOW                  * 40000020
.*                                                                    * 42000020
.*&NAME  LA    1,128                    LOAD FLAG BYTE                * 44000020
